						               													<description>For hundreds of years, brave heroes have kept the peace in the kingdom of Somland.&amp;#10;Delving deep into ancient tombs, driving dragons from the countryside, and vanquishing vile foes of unearthly natures.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;But even heroes take weekends off.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Thus was created that most illustrious of games, golf. Regulated by the Honorable and Ancient Golf Guild Illustrious of Somland (HAGGIS).&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This book contains all the rules you will need to create your hero, select your equipment and then hit the links for a rousing round of golf. Heroes can even gain treasure and experience - if they survive.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The greens of Somland hold great riches for those willing to compete for them. Just beware the dragon sleeping at the 18th hole.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;HAGGIS is a casual &amp;quot;beer and pretzels&amp;quot; style miniatures game about playing golf in a high fantasy world. Players will: create heroes, hire caddies with various special abilities, acquire equipment and magical upgrades. All in an effort to best other players and avoid monsters and hazards on a tabletop fantasy golf course of your design!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Features:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Fun and unique game premise&amp;#10;    Low cost&amp;#10;    Easy to learn&amp;#10;    Requires few miniatures&amp;#10;    Suitable for solo or group play&amp;#10;    Includes campaign rules for character advancement&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
